{"tid":1569001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎教你分擋私了嘅係自己人，左膠定藍廢紙","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T18:05:54.000Z","uid":96371,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6b5a6b6f2d6b7a74368f65e4b3fa4c99d6ef9d","tid":1569001,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單<br />\n根據唔知乜鳩心理學定本能<br />\n人係會將後背交俾佢地信任嘅人，而正面係面向敵人以作防備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以下次大家私了時有人衝出黎擋，如果係面係向自己人後背係對住啲藍廢紙嘅<br />\n大家知佢咩立場同應該點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c30bc990ce21f14ff4d8b74a5bd04cda22f13b","tid":1569001,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f042d39b58ef54d7ddd61ead86519d621d7f2c2","tid":1569001,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1da7309e7514e6606c355d38d05e119969e1d996","tid":1569001,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5dd5135857dc92faa95d0faec21d823606abb3","tid":1569001,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"擋擋擋 擋你呀媽生仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5bb7e44bdb63cffa137b5bb367ebb85e1273e0","tid":1569001,"uid":280648,"like